Paper: hep-th/9911210

Date: 1999-11-25

Title: Null Branes in String Theory Backgrounds

Comments: 11 pages, LaTeX. Final version, to appear in Phys. Rev. D

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D62 (2000) 105001

We consider null bosonic p-branes moving in curved space-times and develop amethod for solving their equations of motion and constraints, which is suitablefor string theory backgrounds. As an application, we give an exact solution forsuch background in ten dimensions.